		<form role='form' method='POST' class='form-inline'>
			<p>If you would like to register with Guernsey Tutors for tutoring, please complete the form below. We will be in touch shortly to organise your first lesson!</p>
			<hr>
			<div class='form-group'>
		      <label for='tutee[name]'>Name</label>
		      <input name="name" class='form-control'>
		    </div>

		    <div class='form-group'>
		      <label for='tutee[email]'>Email</label>
		      <input name="email" class='form-control'>
		    </div>
		    <br>
			<p>Please indicate whether you are a student seeking tutoring, or a parent seeking tutoring for your child:</p>
			<div class="answer-block">
				<input type="radio" name="category" value="student">Student
				<br>
				<input type="radio" name="category" value="parent">Parent
			</div>
            <br>
		    
		    <p>Please give an indication of the subject(s) you wish to cover over your tutoring sessions</p>
		    <div class="answer-block">
			    <input type="checkbox" name="subject" value="maths">Maths
				<br>
				<input type="checkbox" name="subject" value="physics">Physics
				<br>
			    <input type="checkbox" name="subject" value="chemistry">Chemistry
				<br>
				<input type="checkbox" name="subject" value="biology">Biology
			</div>
			<br>

			<p>What exams are you currently preparing for? </p>
			<div class="answer-block">
				<input type="radio" name="level" value="GCSE">GCSE exams or earlier
				<br>
				<input type="radio" name="level" value="AS level">AS levels
				<br>
				<input type="radio" name="level" value="A Level">A levels or university exams
			</div>
			<br>
			
		    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Submit</button>

        </form>
		
